{"tid":957136,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"屌那星，蘋果日報幫高登仔推人氣","createTime":"2018-12-26T19:44:05.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-27T03:53:38.000Z","uid":160807,"like":1,"dislike":19,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"8720456f5e84db0e0ef9cfeb23e520758b61b844","tid":957136,"uid":160807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-26T19:44:05.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20181226/59069271\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181226%2F59069271&d=szw3FXKjsheGnUja62S2fgIBMskQiLF9ooRt%2FFIrCZo%3D&h=80585daa\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181226%2F59069271&h=6f220c1f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20181226/59069271</a><br />\n<br />\n仲突登搞左個節目比佢地<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n【你問我答．精華】 聖誕實戰Speed Dating港女 高登仔：雪好靚 但妳仲靚<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181225/large/1545741838_5124.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181225%2Flarge%2F1545741838_5124.png&h=565fef3f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n「聖誕時節情人冧，路上毒男欲斷魂」，今集《你問我答》請來婚活負責人Anita和Yubi，分享Speed Dating二三事及約會技巧，兩人更與單身已久的高登毒男「阿強」和「樂詩人」同遊海洋公園。當浪漫港女遇上單身毒男，又會擦出甚麼火花？<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：【Chill人生活】台灣「邱比特」雨中配對「絕種MK妹」：是戀愛的感覺啦！<br />\n<br />\n婚活負責人Anita和Yubi說，參加Speed Dating最多的是專業人士，「好多時無時間投放感情，一到大時節就臨急抱佛腳」，當中亦有不少任職空姐、護士、模特兒，甚至藝人的青春少女參加，而女士25、26歲更是最能「包攬」不同年齡層的男士。每到聖誕、農曆新年及情人節等前夕，就是Speed Dating「旺季」。<br />\n<br />\n她們說，Speed Dating普通聚會活動收費每次約300多元，單對單的私人約會收費每次約800至1,000元不等，「（男士）通常參加普通活動，去兩三次已經搞掂。一次活動可能已遇到50個女仔，兩次就遇到100個女仔，好容易响裡面搵到（心儀對象）」。她們提醒，初次見面後如對對方有意，要在一至兩星期內「乘勝追擊」，約會亦會多花心思，了解對方喜好。<br />\n<br />\n有人急尋伴侶，亦有人享受單身。單身分別約8年及4年的高登仔「樂詩人」和「阿強」直言喜歡單身，最「毒」的聖誕節都會躲在家中，打機度過。阿強說，網上不時有人開post大罵港女拜金，雖然自己未遇過，「但都可能有少少潛移默化咗」。<br />\n<br />\n為了讓兩名毒男感受戀愛溫度，Anita和Yubi與二人組成兩對「情侶」，在海洋公園內扔公仔、坐摩天輪、看飄雪。Anita及「阿強」還在旋轉木馬上&hellip;&hellip;唔怕被「閃盲」。讀者可到《蘋果》facebook 、《蘋果》YouTube頻道 ，重溫今集《你問我答》。溫馨提示，本集「關注血糖」人士請小心服用。<br />\n<br />\n鳴謝：海洋公園提供場地及協助 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181225/large/1545743627_293b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181225%2Flarge%2F1545743627_293b.jpg&h=45b05501&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n阿強稱享受單身，至今單身約4年。陳海威、憲威攝"},{"pid":"ff5b41f5f531f5a18b0b6ecb6378f8c10cfdde07","tid":957136,"uid":64374,"like":32,"dislike":2,"score":30,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-26T19:48:38.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e1203a4c7ff7e14697ae20b041c464a173387a9d","tid":957136,"uid":20658,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-26T20:40:58.000Z","msg":"未撚執咩"},{"pid":"3084edd442497e9455476f140c181bee0ada3867","tid":957136,"uid":4917,"like":10,"dislike":3,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-26T20:49:04.000Z","msg":"牙祖marketing囉<br />\n<br />\n之前高登仲係咁同幣少合作添"},{"pid":"7fef518db2f8c6e90abe69a42d8f6e8d3e7a71ba","tid":957136,"uid":1886,"like":5,"dislike":4,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-27T00:21:52.000Z","msg":"HK01, e-zone 呢啲夠成日幫你哋推人氣<br />\n<br />\n高登咁難得上到報就讓下人<br />\n<br />\n咪咁小家啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5456264461c1b35a96bcc559a8aebeeeafc43a3d","tid":957136,"uid":1886,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e1203a4c7ff7e14697ae20b041c464a173387a9d","tid":957136,"uid":20658,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-26T20:40:58.000Z","msg":"未撚執咩"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-2